➜8月当月进出口创历史新高！前8个月山东省进出口由降转升
http://www.sohu.com/a/417101561_100023701	36921
<p><span><span><span>齐鲁网·闪电新闻9月8日讯 </span>据济南</span></span><span><span>、青岛</span></span><span><span>海关统计，</span></span><span><span>今</span></span><span><span>年前</span></span><span><span>8</span></span><span><span>个月</span></span><span><span>，</span></span><span><span>山东省货物贸易进出口</span></span><span><span>1.</span></span><span><span>34</span></span><span><span>万亿元人民币，比去年同期（下同）</span></span><span><span>增长1.5</span></span><span><span>%</span></span><span><span>，</span></span><span><span>扭转</span></span><span><span>今年以来的</span></span><span><span>下降趋势</span></span><span><span>。其中，出口</span></span><span><span>7567.6</span></span><span><span>亿元，增长</span></span><span><span>5.9</span></span><span><span>%</span></span><span><span>；进口</span></span><span><span>5798.</span></span><span><span>8</span></span><span><span>亿元，下降</span></span><span><span>3</span></span><span><span>.8%</span></span><span><span>。贸易顺差</span></span><span><span>1768.7</span></span><span><span>亿元，扩大</span></span><span><span>5</span></span><span><span>8.3</span></span><span><span>%</span></span><span><span>。</span></span></p>
<p><span><span>8</span></span><span><span>月当月，山东省进出口</span></span><span><span>19</span></span><span><span>88.1</span></span><span><span>亿元，增长</span></span><span><span>21</span></span><span><span>%，</span></span><span><span>其中出口</span></span><span><span>1184.8</span></span><span><span>亿元，增长</span></span><span><span>28.2</span></span><span><span>%，</span></span><span><span>进口</span></span><span><span>803.3</span></span><span><span>亿元，增长</span></span><span><span>11.7</span></span><span><span>%</span></span><span><span>。</span></span></p>
<p><span><span>一、前</span></span><span><span>8</span></span><span><span>个月山东省外贸进出口主要特点</span></span></p>
<p><span><span>（一）</span></span><span><span>下半年月度</span></span><span><span>进出口值</span></span><span><span>加速</span></span><span><span>回升，</span></span><span><span>8</span></span><span><span>月进出口值、出口值创历史</span></span><span><span>新</span></span><span><span>高。</span></span><span><span>受新冠疫情影响，年初山东省月度进出口值明显下滑，此后随着省内疫情得到有效控制，复工复产稳步推进，进出口值波动回升</span></span><span><span>，下半年回升速度加快</span></span><span><span>，</span></span><span><span>继</span></span><span><span>7</span></span><span><span>月份</span></span><span><span>创年内新高后，8月份增速继续加快，</span></span><span><span>当月进出口值</span></span><span><span>19</span></span><span><span>88.1亿元，</span></span><span><span>同比</span></span><span><span>增长21</span></span><span><span>%</span></span><span><span>，</span></span><span><span>环比增长</span></span><span><span>3.7</span></span><span><span>%</span></span><span><span>，</span></span><span><span>再创年内新高的同时</span></span><span><span>，也</span></span><span><span>突破历史新高</span></span><span><span>。其中，月度出口值回升势头明显，</span></span><span><span>8</span></span><span><span>月份</span></span><span><span>出口</span></span><span><span>1184.8亿元，</span></span><span><span>同比</span></span><span><span>增长28.2</span></span><span><span>%</span></span><span><span>，</span></span><span><span>环比增长</span></span><span><span>9.6</span></span><span><span>%，</span></span><span><span>进口803.3亿元，</span></span><span><span>同比</span></span><span><span>增长11.7</span></span><span><span>%，环比</span></span><span><span>下降3.9</span></span><span><span>%</span></span><span><span>。</span></span></p>
<p><span><span>（二）山东省进出口增速居主要外贸省市第</span></span><span><span>3</span></span><span><span>位。</span></span><span><span>前</span></span><span><span>8</span></span><span><span>个月，山东省进出口增速在</span></span><span><span>进出口值</span></span><span><span>前</span></span><span><span>10</span></span><span><span>位省市中位列第</span></span><span><span>3</span></span><span><span>位，其中出口、进口增速分别列第</span></span><span><span>3</span></span><span><span>位、第</span></span><span><span>8</span></span><span><span>位</span></span><span><span>。</span></span></p>
<p><span><span>（三）青岛、烟台进出口稳居前列，济南增速较快。</span></span><span><span>前</span></span><span><span>8</span></span><span><span>个月，青岛、烟台进出口值继续位居山东省各地市前列，分别为</span></span><span><span>3955.4</span></span><span><span>亿元和</span></span><span><span>1859.6</span></span><span><span>亿元，分别增长</span></span><span><span>4</span></span><span><span>%</span></span><span><span>和下降</span></span><span><span>1</span></span><span><span>.1%</span></span><span><span>，合计占同期全省进出口总值的</span></span><span><span>43.</span></span><span><span>5</span></span><span><span>%</span></span><span><span>。枣庄</span></span><span><span>、济南、</span></span><span><span>临沂</span></span><span><span>、济宁</span></span><span><span>实现同比两位数增长，增速分别为</span></span><span><span>3</span></span><span><span>8.2</span></span><span><span>%</span></span><span><span>、</span></span><span><span>31.9</span></span><span><span>%</span></span><span><span>、</span></span><span><span>2</span></span><span><span>7.6</span></span><span><span>%</span></span><span><span>、11.7%。</span></span></p>
<p><span><span>（四）一般贸易、保税物流进出口增长，加工贸易进出口下降。</span></span><span><span>前</span></span><span><span>8</span></span><span><span>个月，山东省以一般贸易方式进出口</span></span><span><span>9150.6</span></span><span><span>亿元，增长</span></span><span><span>3.7</span></span><span><span>%</span></span><span><span>，占同期山东省进出口总值的（下同）</span></span><span><span>68.</span></span><span><span>5</span></span><span><span>%</span></span><span><span>；以加工贸易方式进出口</span></span><span><span>2274.1</span></span><span><span>亿元，下降</span></span><span><span>1</span></span><span><span>4.3</span></span><span><span>%</span></span><span><span>，占</span></span><span><span>1</span></span><span><span>7</span></span><span><span>%</span></span><span><span>；以保税物流方式进出口</span></span><span><span>1657.7</span></span><span><span>亿元，增长</span></span><span><span>10.7</span></span><span><span>%</span></span><span><span>。</span></span></p>
<p><span><span>（五）民营企业进出口占比</span></span><span><span>持续</span></span><span><span>提升。</span></span><span><span>前</span></span><span><span>8</span></span><span><span>个月，山东省民营企业进出口</span></span><span><span>9140.4</span></span><span><span>亿元，增长</span></span><span><span>8.2</span></span><span><span>%</span></span><span><span>，占同期山东省进出口总值的</span></span><span><span>68.</span></span><span><span>4</span></span><span><span>%</span></span><span><span>，占比较去年同期提升</span></span><span><span>4.2</span></span><span><span>个百分点；外商投资企业进出口</span></span><span><span>2965.6</span></span><span><span>亿元，下降</span></span><span><span>1</span></span><span><span>4.2</span></span><span><span>%</span></span><span><span>，占</span></span><span><span>22.</span></span><span><span>2</span></span><span><span>%</span></span><span><span>；此外，国有企业进出口</span></span><span><span>1239.1</span></span><span><span>亿元，下降</span></span><span><span>0</span></span><span><span>.1%</span></span><span><span>。</span></span></p>
<p><span><span>（六）对“一带一路”沿线国家进出口增长势头良好。</span></span><span><span>前</span></span><span><span>8</span></span><span><span>个月，山东省对“一带一路”沿线国家进出口</span></span><span><span>4030.6</span></span><span><span>亿元，增长</span></span><span><span>7</span></span><span><span>.5%</span></span><span><span>，占同期山东省进出口总值的</span></span><span><span>30.</span></span><span><span>2</span></span><span><span>%</span></span><span><span>，其中对东盟进出口</span></span><span><span>1729</span></span><span><span>亿元，增长</span></span><span><span>18.7</span></span><span><span>%</span></span><span><span>。同期，对拉丁美洲进出口</span></span><span><span>1589.2</span></span><span><span>亿元，下降</span></span><span><span>1</span></span><span><span>2.2</span></span><span><span>%</span></span><span><span>；对欧盟（不含英国）进出口</span></span><span><span>1431.4</span></span><span><span>亿元，增长</span></span><span><span>7.3</span></span><span><span>%</span></span><span><span>；对美国进出口</span></span><span><span>1315.</span></span><span><span>4</span></span><span><span>亿元，</span></span><span><span>增长</span></span><span><span>1.9%</span></span><span><span>；对韩国进出口</span></span><span><span>1272.3</span></span><span><span>亿元，</span></span><span><span>与去年同期基本持平</span></span><span><span>。此外，对日本进出口</span></span><span><span>983.3</span></span><span><span>亿元，增长</span></span><span><span>2.4</span></span><span><span>%</span></span><span><span>；对非洲进出口</span></span><span><span>939.5</span></span><span><span>亿元，下降</span></span><span><span>2</span></span><span><span>2</span></span><span><span>.7%</span></span><span><span>。</span></span></p>
<p><span><span>（七）原油、金属矿及矿砂进口下降，机电产品、农产品、消费品进口增长。</span></span><span><span>前</span></span><span><span>8</span></span><span><span>个月，山东省进口原油</span></span><span><span>1648.2</span></span><span><span>亿元，下降</span></span><span><span>1</span></span><span><span>3.9</span></span><span><span>%</span></span><span><span>；进口机电产品</span></span><span><span>1130.9</span></span><span><span>亿元，增长</span></span><span><span>4</span></span><span><span>%</span></span><span><span>；进口金属矿及矿砂</span></span><span><span>935.8</span></span><span><span>亿元，下降</span></span><span><span>2.4</span></span><span><span>%</span></span><span><span>，其中铁矿砂</span></span><span><span>507.5</span></span><span><span>亿元，增长</span></span><span><span>1</span></span><span><span>5.9</span></span><span><span>%</span></span><span><span>，铝矿砂</span></span><span><span>1</span></span><span><span>93</span></span><span><span>亿元，下降</span></span><span><span>1</span></span><span><span>3.7</span></span><span><span>%</span></span><span><span>，铜矿砂</span></span><span><span>1</span></span><span><span>38.8</span></span><span><span>亿元，下降</span></span><span><span>3</span></span><span><span>3</span></span><span><span>.5%</span></span><span><span>；进口农产品</span></span><span><span>765.1</span></span><span><span>亿元，增长</span></span><span><span>8.5</span></span><span><span>%</span></span><span><span>。同期，进口消费品</span></span><span><span>443.7</span></span><span><span>亿元，增长</span></span><span><span>16.6</span></span><span><span>%</span></span><span><span>。</span></span></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
